"text","text":"园来自stock（n.树桩）"},{"type":"entry","text":"euphemistic","headword":"euphemistic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj委婉的"},{"type":"text","text":"[ju:fa'mrstrk]"},{"type":"entry","text":"irreconcilable","headword":"irreconcilable"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.无法调和的，矛盾的(incompatible，conflicting)"},{"type":"text","text":"[t'rekansarlabl]"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：ir（不）+reconcilable（可调和的）→无法调和的"},{"type":"text","text":"The faculty senate warned that, if its recommendations were to go unheeded,"},{"type":"text","text":"the differences between the administration and the teaching staff would be"},{"type":"text","text":"exacerbated and eventually rendered irreconcilable."},{"type":"entry","text":"self-conscious","headword":"self-conscious"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj自觉的：害羞的，不自然的"},{"type":"text","text":"[selfkainfas]"},{"type":"text","text":"awkward, bashful, embarrassed"},{"type":"entry","text":"thrifty","headword":"thrifty"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 节俭的(marked by economy and good management)"},{"type":"text","text":"['θrrfti]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自thrift（n.节约）"},{"type":"entry","text":"inelastic","headword":"inelastic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.无弹性的(inflexible)"},{"type":"text","text":"[xnr’laestrk]"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：in（不）+elastic（有弹性的）→无弹性的"},{"type":"entry","text":"fumigate","headword":"fumigate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 用烟源消毒(to expose to the action of fumes in order to disinflect or kill the vermin)"},{"type":"text","text":"['fju:mrgert]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：fum（烟）+ig（看作ag，做）+ate→用烟熏消毒"},{"type":"entry","text":"perspire","headword":"perspire"},{"type":"text","text":".出汗(to sweat)"},{"type":"text","text":"圈词根记忆：per（贯穿）+spir（呼吸）+e→全身都呼吸→出汗"},{"type":"text","text":"[par'sparar]"},{"type":"entry","text":"obstinateness","headword":"obstinateness"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.[固执，顽[固]"},{"type":"text","text":"[a:bstinatnas]"},{"type":"text","text":"圆来自obstinate（adj.顽固的，固执的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"closet","headword":"closet"},{"type":"definition","text":"adji. 秘密的(closely private) n. 棚(a small room where clothing and personal"},{"type":"text","text":"['kla:zat]"},{"type":"text","text":"objects are kept)"},{"type":"entry","text":"headstrong","headword":"headstrong"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 网复自用的(determined to have one’s own way; obstinate; unruly)"},{"type":"text","text":"['hedstro:n]"},{"type":"text","text":"园组合词：head（头）+strong（强的）→头很强→刚优自用的"}]},{"number":397,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<<GRE词汇精选乱序版"},{"type":"entry","text":"cringe","headword":"cringe"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 畏缩(to shrink from sth. dangerous or painful); 追猫(to act in a timid, servile"},{"type":"text","text":"[krind3]"},{"type":"text","text":"manner; fawn)"},{"type":"note","text":"圆联想记忆：C+ring（响铃）+e→一响铃就退缩→畏缩"},{"type":"text","text":"cringe from因.畏缩"},{"type":"entry","text":"countless","headword":"countless"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 无数的(too numerous to be counted)"},{"type":"text","text":"['kauntlas]"},{"type":"text","text":"incalculable, innumerable, numberless, uncountable"},{"type":"entry","text":"impatience","headword":"impatience"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 不耐烦，焦跟(the quality or state of being impatient)"},{"type":"text","text":"[m'perfns]"},{"type":"text","text":"来自patient（adj有耐心的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"elongate","headword":"elongate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.延长，伸长(to extend the length of)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rlo:ngert]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：e（向外)+long（长的）+ate→向外变长→伸长"},{"type":"entry","text":"unjustifiable","headword":"unjustifiable"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 不合道理的(incapable of being justified or explained)"},{"type":"text","text":"[An'd3Astifarabl]"},{"type":"text","text":"The commission of inquiry censured the senator for his lavish expenditure of"},{"type":"text","text":"public funds, which they found to be unjustifiable."},{"type":"entry","text":"verbosity","headword":"verbosity"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 长(an expressive style that uses excessive words)"},{"type":"text","text":"[v3:r'ba:sati]"},{"type":"text","text":"Her verbosity is always a source of irritation: she never uses a single word"},{"type":"text","text":"when she can substitute a long clause or phrase in its place."},{"type":"entry","text":"self-determination","headword":"self-determination"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 自主, 自决(free choice of one's own acts or states without external compulsion)"},{"type":"text","text":"[,selfds,ts:rmr'nex[n]"},{"type":"entry","text":"naivete","headword":"naivete"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.天真的言行举止（a naive remark or action)：天真无邪(the quality or state of"},{"type":"text","text":"[nar'irvati]"},{"type":"text","text":"being naive)"},{"type":"text","text":"We realized that John was still young and impressionable, but were"},{"type":"text","text":"nevertheless surprised at his naivete."},{"type":"entry","text":"venturesome","headword":"venturesome"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 好冒险的(inclined to court or incur risk or danger);(行为)冒险的(involving"},{"type":"text","text":"['ventfarsam]"},{"type":"text","text":"risk)"},{"type":"entry","text":"animosity","headword":"animosity"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.增恶,仇恨(a feeling of strong dislike or hatred)"},{"type":"text","text":"[aenr'ma:sati]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：anim（生命）+osity（表情况）→生命中充满了爱和恨→仇恨"},{"type":"text","text":"animus, antagonism, enmity, hostility, ranco"},{"type":"entry","text":"expressly","headword":"expressly"},{"type":"definition","text":"adv.清楚地(explicitly);特意地(particularly)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rk'spresli]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自express（v.表达adj.特别的；清楚的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"therapy","headword":"therapy"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 治疗 (therapeutic treatment especially of bodily, mental,"},{"type":"text","text":"[Berapi]"},{"type":"text","text":"or behavioral disorder)"},{"type":"text","text":"inflate"},{"type":"text","text":"The child needed physical therapy to counteract the"},{"type":"text","text":"rigidity that had tragically immobilized his legs."},{"type":"entry","text":"inflate","headword":"inflate"},{"type":"text","text":".使充气，使膨胀（to fil with air）"}]},{"number":398,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 36 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"charitable","headword":"charitable"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 行善的(full of love for and goodwill toward others); 仁爱的(liberal in"},{"type":"text","text":"['t{eratabl]"},{"type":"text","text":"benefactions to the needy)"},{"type":"text","text":"benevolent, clement, humanitarian, lenient, philanthropic"},{"type":"entry","text":"stronghold","headword":"stronghold"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 要塞(a fortified place); 堡垒，根据地(a place of security or survival)"},{"type":"text","text":"['stro:nhauld]"},{"type":"text","text":"fortress"},{"type":"entry","text":"venomous","headword":"venomous"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 有毒的(full of venom; poisonous)"},{"type":"text","text":"[venamas]"},{"type":"text","text":"deadlly, vicious, virulent"},{"type":"entry","text":"mysticism","headword":"mysticism"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 神秘主义(immediate consciousness of the transcendent or ultimate reality)"},{"type":"text","text":"[mrstrsizam]"},{"type":"text","text":"No longer sustained by the belief that the world around us was expressly"},{"type":"text","text":"designed for humanity, many people try to find intellectual substitutes for that"},{"type":"text","text":"lost certainty in astrology and in mysticism."},{"type":"entry","text":"dumbfound","headword":"dumbfound"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.使惊讶（to astonish)"},{"type":"text","text":"[dam'faund]"},{"type":"text","text":"园组合词：dumb（哑）+found（被发现）→惊讶得说不出话来→使惊讶"},{"type":"text","text":"amaze, astound"},{"type":"entry","text":"nonporous","headword":"nonporous"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad.无孔的：不渗透的"},{"type":"text","text":"[na:n'p>:ras]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：non（不）+porous（多孔的：能渗透的）→无孔的：不渗透的"},{"type":"entry","text":"bonanza","headword":"bonanza"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 富矿脉，贵金属矿(an exceptionally large and rich mineral deposit)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ba'naenza]"},{"type":"text","text":"eldorado, golconda"},{"type":"entry","text":"transitoriness","headword":"transitoriness"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.暂时，短暂(the state of being not persistent)"},{"type":"text","text":"['transat:rinas]"},{"type":"text","text":"Parts of seventeenth-century Chinese pleasure gardens were not necessarily"},{"type":"text","text":"intended to look cheerful; they were designed expressly to evoke the agreeable"},{"type":"text","text":"melancholy resulting from a sense of the transitoriness of natural beauty and"},{"type":"text","text":"human glory."},{"type":"entry","text":"restatement","headword":"restatement"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.再声明，重述"},{"type":"text","text":"[ri:'stertmant]"},{"type":"entry","text":"infest","headword":"infest"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 大批出没于，骚扰(to spread or swarm in or over in a troublesome manner);"},{"type":"text","text":"[in'fest]"},{"type":"text","text":"奇生于(to live in or on as a parasite)"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：in（使）+fest（仇恨）→骚扰"},{"type":"entry","text":"hunch","headword":"hunch"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.直觉，预感（an intuitive feeling or a premonition)"},{"type":"text","text":"[hAnt]"},{"type":"text","text":"have a hunch（that)有预感（将发生-)"},{"type":"entry","text":"regulatory","headword":"regulatory"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad按规矩来的，依照规章的：调整的"},{"type":"text","text":"['regjalab:ri]"},{"type":"entry","text":"audit","headword":"audit"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 旁听(to attend (a course) without working for or expecting to receive formal"}]},{"number":399,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"unbecoming","headword":"unbecoming"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 不合身的(not suited to the wearer); 不得体的(improper)"},{"type":"text","text":"[Anbr'kAmrn]"},{"type":"text","text":"国联想记忆：un（不）+becoming（合适的）→不合身的"},{"type":"entry","text":"flaggy","headword":"flaggy"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.枯萎的：松软无力的（lacking vigor orforce）"},{"type":"text","text":"['flaegi]"},{"type":"entry","text":"earthiness","headword":"earthiness"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 土质，土性(the state of earth)"},{"type":"text","text":"['3:rBinas]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自earthy（adj.泥土的，土的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"foreshadow","headword":"foreshadow"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.成为先兆，预示（to represent, indicate,or typify beforehand)"},{"type":"text","text":"[fo:r'faedau]"},{"type":"text","text":"组合词：fore（预先）+shadow（影子）→影子先来→预示"},{"type":"entry","text":"institutionalized","headword":"institutionalized"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 制度化的的(making into an institution)"},{"type":"text","text":"[Instr'tu:{analatzd]"},{"type":"text","text":"As the creation of new knowledge through science has become"},{"type":"text","text":"institutionalizec resistance to innovation has become less aggressive taking the"},{"type":"text","text":"form of inertia rather than direct attack."},{"type":"entry","text":"pitcher","headword":"pitcher"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 有柄水罐(a container for liquids that usually has a handle)"},{"type":"text","text":"['prtfar]"},{"type":"text","text":"jug"},{"type":"entry","text":"reaffirm","headword":"reaffirm"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 再次确定(confirm again);重申(to state again positively)"},{"type":"text","text":"[,ri:a'fs:rm]"},{"type":"note","text":"图联想记忆：re（再次）+affirm（确定）→再次确定"},{"type":"entry","text":"infinitesimal","headword":"infinitesimal"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.极微小的(infinitely small) n.极小量"},{"type":"text","text":"[,rnfrnx'tesrml]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：in（不）+finite（有限的）+sim（百分之一）+al→无"},{"type":"text","text":"hieroglyph"},{"type":"text","text":"限小的→极微小的"},{"type":"entry","text":"hieroglyph","headword":"hieroglyph"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.象形文字，神秘符号（a picture or symbol used in"},{"type":"text","text":"['hararaglif]"},{"type":"text","text":"hieroglyphic writing)"},{"type":"text","text":"圈词根记忆：hier（神圣的）+o+glyph（写，刻）→神写的字→"},{"type":"text","text":"神秘符号"},{"type":"entry","text":"transcribe","headword":"transcribe"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.抄写，转录(to make a writen copy)"},{"type":"text","text":"[traen'skrarb]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：trans（转移）+（s）cribe（写）→写到别的地方→抄写"},{"type":"entry","text":"grandiloquence","headword":"grandiloquence"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 豪言壮语，夸张之言(a lofty. extravagantly colorful, pompous, or bombastic"},{"type":"text","text":"[graen'drlakwans]"},{"type":"text","text":"style, manner, or quality especially in language)"},{"type":"entry","text":"picturesque","headword":"picturesque"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.如画的（resembling a picture);独特的，别具风格的(charming or quaint in"},{"type":"text","text":"[prktfa'resk]"},{"type":"text","text":"appearance)"},{"type":"entry","text":"unspoiled","headword":"unspoiled"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj未损坏的，未宠坏的"},{"type":"text","text":"[An'sporld]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：un（不）+spoil(损坏）+ed→未损坏的"},{"type":"entry","text":"nonradioactive","headword":"nonradioactive"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj非放射性的"},{"type":"text","text":"[nan'rerdiau'ektrv]"},{"type":"text","text":"国联想记忆：non（不）+radioactive(故射性的）→非放射性的"},{"type":"text","text":"nonradioactive labeling 非放射性标记"},{"type":"entry","text":"rag","headword":"rag"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 旧布，碎布(old cloth);破旧衣服(an old worn-out garment)"},{"type":"text","text":"[raeg]"},{"type":"text","text":"lose one'srag发怒，生气"},{"type":"text","text":"天場下来"},{"type":"entry","text":"modifier","headword":"modifier"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.修改者（one that modifies);修饰语（a word or phrase"},{"type":"text","text":"高个顶着"},{"type":"text","text":"['ma:drfarar]"},{"type":"text","text":"that makes specific the meaning of another word or phrase)"},{"type":"entry","text":"optimistic","headword":"optimistic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 乐观的(believing that good things will happen in the"},{"type":"text","text":"[a:ptt'mrstrk]"},{"type":"text","text":"future)"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：optim（最好的）+istic→最好的→乐观的"}]},{"number":400,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 36 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"paleolithic","headword":"paleolithic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. I旧石器时代的(of or relating to the earliest period of the Stone Age"},{"type":"text","text":"[paelia'lrθrk]"},{"type":"text","text":"characterized by rough or chipped stone implements)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：paleo（古老的）+lith（石头）+ic→|旧石器的→旧石器时代的"},{"type":"entry","text":"digressive","headword":"digressive"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.离题的，枝节的(characterized by digressions)"},{"type":"text","text":"[dar'gresiv]"},{"type":"text","text":"digressive remarks 离题的言论"},{"type":"entry","text":"snug","headword":"snug"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 温暖舒适的(warm and comfortable; cozy)"},{"type":"text","text":"[snAg]"},{"type":"text","text":"图snugharbor避风港"},{"type":"entry","text":"murderous","headword":"murderous"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj 蓄意谋杀的，凶残的(having the purpose or capabity of murder);厉害的，"},{"type":"text","text":"['ms:rdaras]"},{"type":"text","text":"要命的(having the ability or power to overwhelm)"},{"type":"entry","text":"tricky","headword":"tricky"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 猬的(inclined to or marked by trickery)"},{"type":"text","text":"[traki]"},{"type":"text","text":"crafty, cunning"},{"type":"entry","text":"vent","headword":"vent"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.发泄（感情，尤指愤怒)(to discharge;expel)：开孔（to provide with a vent)"},{"type":"text","text":"[vent]"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 子孔, 口(an opening)"},{"type":"entry","text":"raisin","headword":"raisin"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 葡萄干(a grape that has been dried)"},{"type":"text","text":"['reizn]"},{"type":"entry","text":"defrost","headword":"defrost"},{"type":"definition","text":"v 解冻(to release from a frozen state)：将-除霜(to free from ice)"},{"type":"text","text":"[,di:fro:st]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：de（除去）+frost（霜冻）→将霜除去→解冻"},{"type":"entry","text":"atomic","headword":"atomic"},{"type":"text","text":"adlj. 原子的(of, relating to, or concerned with atoms);微数小的(minute)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'ta:mik]"},{"type":"text","text":"来自atom（v原子）"},{"type":"entry","text":"intemperance","headword":"intemperance"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.放纵，不节制，过度（lack of temperance)"},{"type":"text","text":"[In'temparans]"},{"type":"text","text":"excess, overindulgence, surfeit"},{"type":"entry","text":"untutored","headword":"untutored"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 未受教育的(having no formal learning or training)"},{"type":"text","text":"[An'tu:tard]"},{"type":"entry","text":"affordable","headword":"affordable"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 负担得起的(being able to buy sth.)"},{"type":"text","text":"[afo:rdabl]"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：afford(买得起）+able（adj.能）→负担得起的"},{"type":"entry","text":"modulate","headword":"modulate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.调整，调节(to adjust to or keep in proper measure or proportion; regulate by"},{"type":"text","text":"['ma:d3alert]"},{"type":"text","text":"or adjust to): 调音( to tune to a key or pitch)"},{"type":"entry","text":"misogyny","headword":"misogyny"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.厌恶女人(hatred of women)"},{"type":"text","text":"[mr'sa:d3ini]"},{"type":"text","text":"Strindberg's plays are marked by his extreme misogyny; he felt modern"},{"type":"text","text":"woman needed to dominate man and by subordinating him invalidate his"},{"type":"text","text":"masculinity."},{"type":"entry","text":"brownish","headword":"brownish"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad成褐色的"},{"type":"text","text":"['braunx]"},{"type":"text","text":"来自brown（n.揭色）"},{"type":"entry","text":"coercion","headword":"coercion"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.强制，高压统治（the act,process,or power of coercing)"},{"type":"text","text":"[kau’s:r3n]"},{"type":"text","text":"compulsion, constraint, enforcement"},{"type":"entry","text":"economize","headword":"economize"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.节约，节省（to save)"}]},{"number":40