ype":"entry","text":"negotiable","headword":"negotiable"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 可协商的(capable of being negotiated); 可通行的"},{"type":"text","text":"navigable, passable"},{"type":"text","text":"念"},{"type":"text","text":"[nr'gaufiabl]"},{"type":"text","text":"碑"},{"type":"entry","text":"monumental","headword":"monumental"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 极大的(massive; impressively large);纪念碑的(built"},{"type":"text","text":"[ma:nju'ment]"},{"type":"text","text":"as a monument)"},{"type":"text","text":"图来自monument（n.纪念碑）"},{"type":"entry","text":"gusher","headword":"gusher"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.溶不绝的说话者(a person who gushes);喷油井(an oil well)"},{"type":"text","text":"['gAfar]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自gush（v.喷出，涌出：滔溶不绝地说话）"},{"type":"entry","text":"levy","headword":"levy"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 征税(to impose a tax); 征兵(to draft into military service)"},{"type":"text","text":"[levi]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：lev（提高）+y→提高（政府收入）→征税"},{"type":"entry","text":"cumber","headword":"cumber"},{"type":"definition","text":"v 拖累, 奶妨码(to hinder by obstruction or interference; hamper)"},{"type":"text","text":"['kAmbar]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：cumb（躺）+er→躺着不动→拖累，妨碍"}]}]}